Marriages and issue.
He married  <START:person> Aminā <END>  ( <START:person> Emine <END> ) Mihr-î-Mâh Sultan and Râbi'a Sermi Sultan.
By the first wife he had  <START:person> Mustafa III <END>  and by the second wife he had  <START:person> Abdul Hamid I. <END> 
