 <START:person> Ayer <END>  was married four times to three women.
His first marriage was from 1932–1941 to (Grace Isabel)  <START:person> Renée <END>  (d.
1980), who subsequently married philosopher  <START:person> Stuart Hampshire <END> ,  <START:person> Ayer <END> 's friend and colleague.
