 <START:person> Amerigo Vespucci <END>  was born and raised in Florence, Italy.
He was the third son of  <START:person> Ser Nastagio <END>  ( <START:person> Anastasio <END> ), a Florentine notary, and Lisabetta Mini.
 <START:person> Amerigo Vespucci <END>  was educated by his uncle,  <START:person> Fra Giorgio Antonio Vespucci <END> , a Dominican friar of the monastery of San Marco in Florence.
